===Etymology 1===
From {{inh|en|enm|yeer}}, {{m|enm|yere}}, from {{inh|en|ang|ġēar||year}}, from {{inh|en|gmw-pro|*jār}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*jērą||year}}, from {{inh|en|ine-pro|*yóh₁r̥|t=year, spring}}.
